{{version028}}
{{flavour|Causes a strong gust of wind, pushing away creatures and clouds in a cone.}}
'''Wind Blast''' is a monster-only spell which projects a massive gust of wind at the player and all their allies, shoving them away from the caster. This inflicts no damage, but can make maneuvering around a battle or standing your ground in a safe choke point extremely difficult. It cannot force its victim to enter [[deep water]] or [[lava]].

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.27]], the spell could push [[flying]] targets further away.
*Prior to [[0.25]], a similar effect was available to the player via the [[fan of gales]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
